snippet.description:

Two colleagues who become stranded on a deserted island, the only survivors of a plane crash. On the island, they must overcome past grievances and work together to survive, but ultimately, it's a battle of wills and wits to make it out alive.

Send Help (2026) is the new horror movie by Sam Raimi, starring Rachel McAdams, Dylan O'Brien and Dennis Haysbert. The script was written by Damian Shannon & Mark Swift..
